    • Method Detail

      • createMessaging

        public abstract void createMessaging()
        Asynchronous call to create a Xively Messaging Service instance. The clean session is set to true, and there is no last will set. The service will be returned as a parameter of the serviceCreated event of the XiServiceCreatorCallback. Service Creator Callback listeners must registered before this method is called.

      • createMessaging

        public abstract void createMessaging(boolean cleanSession)
        Asynchronous call to create a Xively Messaging Service instance. The clean session can be set, and there is no last will. The service will be returned as a parameter of the serviceCreated event of the XiServiceCreatorCallback. Service Creator Callback listeners must registered before this method is called.

      • createMessaging

        public abstract void createMessaging(boolean cleanSession,
                                     XiLastWill lastWill)
        Asynchronous call to create a Xively Messaging Service instance. Both the clean session and the last will can be set. The service will be returned as a parameter of the serviceCreated event of the XiServiceCreatorCallback. Service Creator Callback listeners must registered before this method is called.
